name: Archery
display_help: The ancient art of Archery allows you to use a Bow and Arrow to great effect. This power set has an inherent bonus to Accuracy.

name: Assault_Rifle
display_help: The Assault Rifle is a state-of-the-art piece of hardware. It is equipped to handle an impressive arsenal of munitions and firing modes. The Assault Rifle is also equipped with the latest in targeting technology, and is a very accurate weapon.

name: Battle_Axe
display_help: You can wield a Battle Axe and master a variety of powerful Lethal attacks. Battle Axe is a slow but powerful weapon that has a tendency to send foes flying. This massive weapon has a bonus to hit.

name: Beam_Rifle
display_help: Your weapon of choice is a high tech beam rifle capable of firing a wide variety of energy blasts at your foes. Your Beam Rifle attacks will have greater effect while Disintegration is in effect on your target. Beam Rifle focuses on dealing a great deal of single target damage, but has a few area of effect attacks as well.

name: Brawling
display_help: Street Justice delivers punishing bone crushing attacks that weaken, disable or otherwise hinder their foes. This melee power set has no singular form of secondary effect. Instead, it has many ways to cripple enemies. Street Justice's attack powers come in two categories: Combo Builders and Finishers. Combo Builders add to your Combo Level and thus empower any Finishers you use. See individual powers for how they're improved by Combo Level. Combo Building powers can provide up to 3 levels of benefits. Build up to the third level before executing a Finisher for maximum effectiveness.

name: Broad_Sword
display_help: Wield a Broad Sword and master a variety of powerful Lethal attacks. Slower than a Katana, the Broad Sword's weight strikes with more force and damage. The Broadsword can reduce an enemy's Defense, allowing other attacks to hit more reliably. The Broad Sword is a powerful melee weapon that has a bonus to Accuracy. Like all scrapper powers, all Broad Sword attacks can sometimes land a critical hit for double damage.

name: Claws
display_help: Claws are bones or blades that extend from your hands and cause Lethal damage. The lightweight, natural feel of claws gives this power set a reduced Endurance cost and faster attack rate than other Scrapper melee sets. Like all scrapper powers, all Claw attacks can sometimes land a critical hit for double damage.

name: Cold_Domination
display_help: Cold Domination powers allow you to manipulate cold and ice to protect your allies and weaken your enemies.

name: Dark_Armor
display_help: Dark Armor allows you to tap into the powers of the Netherworld for protection. Many Dark Armor powers drain your foes to strengthen you. Dark Armor offers very good resistance to Negative Energy damage, and is one of the only defensive sets that offer some resistance to Psionic damage. However, its resistance to Energy is weak and it offers no protection from Knockback or Immobilization.

name: Dark_Assault
display_help: Blind and drain your foes with dark energies. Dark Assault allows you to pummel your foes with heavy hitting melee attacks as well as several ranged attacks. Many of Dark Assaults powers reduce their victims' chance to hit.

name: Dark_Blast
display_help: Dark Blast summons the powers of the Netherworld to defeat your foes. The draining effects of most of these powers can reduce your targets' chance to hit.

name: Dark_Melee
display_help: Dark Melee allows you to focus the powers of the Netherworld to defeat your foes. The draining effects of most of these powers can reduce the target's Accuracy.

name: Dark_Miasma
display_help: Focus the dark power of the Netherworld to weaken your foes. Dark Miasma focuses on draining your opponent.

name: Darkness_Control
display_help: You can control darkness and shadow to disable your foes with negative energy. Enemies that are affected by many of your attacks will have their chance to hit reduced.

name: Darkness_Manipulation
display_help: Assail your foes with powers drawn from the abyss. Darkness Manipulation offers powers that can both control and heavily damage their targets while reducing their chance to hit.

name: Dual_Blades
display_help: You are a master of fighting with a blade in each hand. Your precision and skill with the blades enable you to strike in numerous combinations, each of which has unique secondary effects on a target which withstands your onslaught.

name: Dual_Pistols
display_help: You're a master of akimbo pistols, wielding a high caliber fire arm in each hand. Your attacks primarily deal lethal damage and you have a wide variety of attacks, however your strength lies within your ability to use your "Ammo Swap" power to change out your ammo mid-battle. Doing so can change your secondary damage type and effects making you an incredibly versatile ranged combatant.

name: Earth_Assault
display_help: With Earth Assault, you can damage foes with the very ground they walk upon. You can conjure stone weapons, hurl boulders, and even cause magma to erupt from the ground.

name: Earth_Control
display_help: You can control the forces of the Earth. You can manipulate earth and stone to defeat your foes. The crushing force of many Earth Powers can reduce a target's Defense. Being of the Earth, many of these powers need to be performed while on the ground.

name: Electric_Armor
display_help: Your entire body is basically a powerful capacitor. You can store and release massive amounts of electricity that can absorb damage directed at you. Electric Armor offer better than average resistance to just about all types of damage, including Psionic, but has no healing abilities or resistance to Toxic. Electric Armor also offers superior resistance to Energy damage and Endurance Drain.

name: Electric_Control
display_help: Electricity leaps and sparks at your command. You can use raw electrical power to paralyze, knockdown and drain the endurance of foes.

name: Electrical_Blast
display_help: Electrical Blast endows you with ranged electrical attack powers. Electrical powers can drain foes' Endurance and can often temporarily halt their Endurance recovery. This can be quite effective against higher level foes and Bosses. Some Electrical Blast powers can even sometimes transfer this Endurance back to you.

name: Electrical_Melee
display_help: Electricity surges through your body and you can channel this electricity through your fists. Electrical Melee allows you to pummel your foes with various melee attack powers while jolting them with a powerful electric current. Electric Melee powers can drain foes' Endurance and temporarily halt their Endurance recovery. Some powers may even return a portion of drained Endurance back to you.

name: Electricity_Assault
display_help: Electrical Assault grants you several electrical ranged and melee powers. Electrical powers can drain foes' Endurance and can often temporarily halt their Endurance recovery. This can be quite effective against higher level foes and Bosses. Some Electrical Assault powers can even sometimes transfer this Endurance back to you.

name: Electricity_Manipulation
display_help: Electricity Manipulation empowers you with various electrical melee attack and support powers. Electricity Manipulation powers can drain foes' Endurance and temporarily halt their Endurance recovery. Some powers return a portion of drained Endurance to you.

name: Empathy
display_help: Empathy gives you the ability to heal and aid allies as well as yourself. Empathy has no offensive powers, but its heals and buffs are unmatched.

name: Energy_Assault
display_help: Focus pure energy into deadly melee attacks and powerful projectiles. The impact of the melee powers can often Disorient opponents, while the velocity of the ranged projectiles can send your enemies flying.

name: Energy_Aura
display_help: You can surround yourself in powerful defensive Energy Auras that can deflect your foes' attacks. Like other defensive powers, Energy Auras do not reduce the damage you take, but rather reduce your chance of getting hit by deflecting your foes' attacks. Energy Auras offer good defense to most attack types, but offer superior defense to Energy based attacks. However, Energy Aura offers no defense to Psionic attacks.

name: Energy_Blast
display_help: Energy Blast allows you to hurl bolts of energy at your foes, and can often send them flying with Knockback.

name: Energy_Manipulation
display_help: Energy Manipulation allows you to channel energy to deliver deadly blows. These powers also help you focus your power to increase your own abilities.

name: Energy_Melee
display_help: You can use Energy Melee to power your blows with pure energy. These focused power attacks often Disorient opponents.

name: Fiery_Assault
display_help: Fiery Assault allows you to conjure up flaming melee attacks and hurl devastating fiery projectiles. Fiery Assault powers tend to set foes ablaze for added Damage Over Time.

name: Fiery_Aura
display_help: Through intense heat and fire, you can absorb many kinds of damage. Fiery Aura offers superior resistance to Fire damage, but weak resistance to Cold damage and no protection to Knockback. Fiery Aura is the most offensive of the Tanker's defensive Power Sets, offering some damage output.

name: Fiery_Melee
display_help: Fiery Melee allows you to attack with fire, and even conjure up flaming melee weapons. Fiery Melee powers tend to set foes ablaze for added Damage Over Time.

name: Fire_Blast
display_help: Fire Blast allows you to blast fire at foes, with a tendency to set them ablaze for added damage over time.

name: Fire_Control
display_help: You can control the essence of fire to entrap, scorch, and manipulate your foes with smoke and flame.

name: Fire_Manipulation
display_help: Fire Manipulation lets you surround yourself with various manifestations of fire and flames, assaulting and burning nearby foes. Fire Manipulation powers tend to set foes ablaze for added damage over time.

name: Force_Field
display_help: The Force Field powers give you the ability to create shells of energy that protect yourself and your allies from various forms of damage and harm. Force Fields do not reduce damage, but reduced your allies chance of getting hit in the first place.

name: Gadgets
display_help: Devices are equipment you have constructed for use in combat. By using them strategically, you can gain a great tactical advantage. Traps, non-lethal munitions, and demolitions are available in this power set.

name: Gravity_Control
display_help: This power set allows you to manipulate the forces of gravity to control your foes. Enemies have little defense against Gravity powers.

name: Ice_Armor
display_help: You can dramatically reduce your core body temperature to form various armors of ice around yourself. You can protect yourself from many different damage types, and you gain exceptional resistance to Cold based attacks. However, this set offers little protection to Fire based powers and no protection against Psionics.

name: Ice_Blast
display_help: Ice Blast allows you to use the power of ice against your foes, with a tendency to Slow their attacks and movement.

name: Ice_Control
display_help: You can draw moisture from the air to create Icy formations. With these abilities, you can control ice with remarkable precision to dominate your foes.

name: Ice_Manipulation
display_help: Ice Manipulation lets you surround yourself with various manifestations of ice and cold, assaulting and freezing nearby foes. Ice Manipulation powers are known to Slow opponents.

name: Ice_Melee
display_help: Ice Melee allows the player to use Cold-based attacks, and even conjure up frozen melee weapons. Ice Melee powers are known for their ability to slow an opponent.

name: Icy_Assault
display_help: Ice Assault allows the player to use Cold-based attacks. Conjure up frozen melee weapons or hurl deadly shards of Ice. Icy powers are known for their ability to slow an opponent.

name: Illusion_Control
display_help: You can manipulate light and sound to manifest all sorts of Illusions, aiding your allies as well as deceiving your foes.

name: Invulnerability
display_help: Invulnerability gives you incredible abilities to resist damage and other effects. Its resistance to physical damage is superior, however, Invulnerability offers no protection from Psionic attacks.

name: Katana
display_help: Wield a Katana and master a variety of powerful Lethal attacks. A quick and elegant weapon, the Katana is faster than a Broad Sword, and can reduce an enemy's Defense. The Katana is a fine blade that always has a bonus to Accuracy. Like all scrapper powers, all Katana attacks can sometimes land a critical hit for double damage.

name: Kinetic_Attack
display_help: Kinetic Melee features a mix of fast light attacks and slow heavy attacks, including some with range. All attacks in this set reduce the damage strength of enemies who are hit.

name: Kinetics
display_help: You are a master at manipulating and transferring Kinetic energy. You can manipulate the potential energy found in objects to aid your allies or weaken your foes.

name: Martial_Arts
display_help: A compilation of various fighting techniques from around the world, Martial Arts makes you a master in the art of hand to hand combat. Martial Artists tend to be very accurate with their strikes. Like all scrapper powers, all Martial Arts attacks can sometimes land a critical hit for double damage.

name: Mental_Manipulation
display_help: Manipulate your enemies with an array of offensive Psionic powers. Few living beings can resist their effects. Creatures without minds, however, like machines and robots, are much more resistant.

name: Mind_Control
display_help: You can manipulate and control your opponent's mind. Since Mental powers directly affect the mind, most tend to be very accurate, and thus very useful against higher level foes. Few foes can resist Psionic powers, but creatures without minds, like machines and robots, are resistant to many of the effects.

name: Ninjitsu
display_help: Ninjitsu is the secret art of Ninja. Many Ninjitsu powers emphasize acute senses that allow you to react deftly to avoid danger. Others focus on the ability to hide in plain sight. Still others rely on the ancient art of Kuji Kiri, and the pure focus of the mind to accomplish the impossible.

name: Pain_Domination
display_help: Pain Domination gives a character the ability to manipulate, nullify and amplify pain. Ultimately this grants the user powerful healing, buffing and debuffing powers. It's healing output is unmatched!

name: Plant_Control
display_help: You can call forth and control the power of plants and flora to control your foes. Animate and control vines, roots and spores to entrap, entwine and utterly dominate your foes. Many Plant Control powers are only effective if the target is near the ground.

name: Poison
display_help: You are a master of Poison and can concoct a variety of venoms and toxins allowing you to weaken your enemies. When used correctly, some Poisons can even be used to aid your allies.

name: Psionic_Assault
display_help: Blast your enemies with an array of offensive Psionic powers. Few living beings can resist their effects. Creatures without minds, however, like machines and robots, are much more resistant.

name: Psychic_Blast
display_help: Blast villains with an array of offensive, long range Psionic powers. While few living beings can resist their effects, Creatures without minds, like machines and robots, are not affected as strongly.

name: Radiation_Blast
display_help: Blast your foes with lethal radiation. Radiation Blast powers can bypass normal defenses, and lower your targets' overall Defense.

name: Radiation_Emission
display_help: Radiation Emission powers allow you to manipulate atomic particles and waves to protect your allies and weaken your enemies.

name: Regeneration
display_help: Regeneration lets you regenerate more quickly from damage and effects. Regeneration offers almost no actual damage resistance, but your Hit Point Regeneration can become so incredibly fast, that your wounds heal almost instantly. Those who possess this power set have little downtime.

name: Shield_Defense
display_help: Your mastery over the shield protects you from all forms of attacks in the form of defense as well as some moderate damage resistance to most types of damage. Your training with the shield enables you to protect your nearby allies boosting their defenses.

name: Sonic_Attack
display_help: Sonic Attack lets you use the power of sound waves to damage and weaken your foes.

name: Sonic_Debuff
display_help: You have the ability to control sound in several fashions. You can create semi-solid barriers, set up waves which weaken or strengthen a target, as well as creating soothing sounds which act to counteract any negative effects which may exist on your friends.

name: Spines
display_help: Spines protrude from your body and can deal damage in melee or at very short ranges. Spines are hollow and hold a neural toxin that deals additional Toxic damage and can Slow or Immobilize your enemies. The toxin is cumulative, and multiple hits will affect a target more strongly. Very few foes have resistance to Spine poison. Like all scrapper powers, all Spine attacks can sometimes land a critical hit for double damage.

name: Staff_Fighting
display_help: You have mastered the art of staff fighting, allowing you to strike at your foes in great sweeping arcs. Staff Fighting provides a good amount of control effects as well as some self buffs. By selecting the Staff Mastery power, you will gain access to techniques that further empower your Staff Fighting techniques and grant you useful augmentations that build up as you fight.

name: Stone_Armor
display_help: You can transform your skin into various forms of rock and stone. Stone Armor is one of the only Tanker Defensive Power Sets that offers defense to Psionics. Stone Armor offers amazing Defense, but a few Stone Armors are mutually exclusive to each other. Some Armors, although offering superior defense, also slow you down due to its enormous bulk.

name: Stone_Melee
display_help: You can use the powers of earth and stone to do battle with your foes. Stone Melee allows you to strike with fists of stone, summon earthen weapons, and even quake the very ground itself.

name: Storm_Summoning
display_help: You can command the forces of nature! Storm Summoning allows you to control wind and weather to aid your allies and wreak havoc on your foes.

name: Super_Reflexes
display_help: Your Super Reflexes and acute senses allow you to react deftly to avoid danger. Regardless of what comes at you, Super Reflexes simply allows you to avoid the attack. The type of weapon or attack used against you is irrelevant. So swords, bullets, fire, energy, even Psionic Attacks can be avoided. Super Reflexes focuses on different techniques. Avoiding melee attacks is different than avoiding ranged attacks or even area-of-effect attacks. Your weakness is your opponents accuracy.

name: Super_Strength
display_help: Super Strength gives you combat powers derived from your super-human physical strength. Super Strength powers tend to knock foes back.

name: Thermal_Radiation
display_help: You have the ability to control heat and Thermal Radiation. This allows you to protect allies from harm, heal them or increase their abilities. You can also weaken your enemies.

name: Thorny_Assault
display_help: Thorns protrude from your body and can deal damage in melee or at range. Thorns are hollow and inject toxin that deals additional Toxic damage and can weaken your enemy's Defense. Very few foes have resistance to Thorn toxins.

name: Time_Manipulation
display_help: By gazing into the flow of time you are able to manipulate time itself. Time Manipulation allows the wielder to inflict crippling debuffs, buff and heal allies and also be able to empower effects on single targets through careful use of Time Crawl and Temporal Selection.

name: Titan_Weapons
display_help: You wield an over-sized weapon of some sort; a gigantic sword, mace or axe or possibly even a railroad crossing sign. The weapon's sheer mass gives it great destructive power, and your immense strength and skill allow you to use it as a devastating weapon. Titan Weapons as a set, has exceptional area of effect capability, while retaining a strong single target ability. Certain powers can only be used as follow up attacks and are grayed out when first entering combat, while others allow you to build up momentum and accelerate your attack speed for a few moments.

name: Trick_Arrow
display_help: Trick Arrows are tipped with an odd variety of payloads, which if used strategically, can dramatically alter a battle site.

name: War_Mace
display_help: You can wield a Medieval Mace and master a variety of powerful Smashing attacks. Attack speeds are good, and the weight of the Mace has good Disorienting capabilities. The sheer weight of this weapon give it a bonus to hit.

name: Willpower
display_help: You aren't Invulnerable. Bullets don't bounce off of you, and if you are cut, you bleed. You are, however, tough, grizzled and strong willed. It takes more than a little cut to keep you down! Willpower offers a strong balance of healing, damage resistance and defense. While you have no real vulnerabilities, you can't quite deal with 'alpha strikes' as well as some other protective powers.
